Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋  伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可过不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不能前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过去不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋  伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哟  有路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是帮大忙了  接着走  接着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着走  接着走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个轿子也跟骨灰盒差不多大小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  赶快把主公抬到身体那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  门缝夹着张纸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸人形？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师  你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡逻啦  巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找有没有想算计你  一口把你吃掉的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  夹在门缝里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！  夏目～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  有股很强的力量在拉扯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  好痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把施过法术的纸人形夹在你家门缝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你回来了就飞回来找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是迟钝啊  被它缠上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是你弄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生是在私下进行驱除妖怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  在这里站着说话也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上则是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取周一？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当前很红的演员  名取周一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  他有点烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的长假  你有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢温泉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去温泉旅馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在芳香剂的抽奖活动里中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉住宿双人券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳香剂？  抽奖？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  怎么要来找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个女孩子去如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们事务所不准这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙每次都让人觉得可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  把这家伙做成天妇罗让我吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有男性的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  能看见相同景色的就只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一次都没去过旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那间旅馆可以带宠物的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！去吧夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋～蛋～温泉蛋～夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家人那边就由我去说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  旅行？真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会负起责任  照顾好夏目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这么可靠的朋友去就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天来接他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志你总是在跟我们客气  这次我有点高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你就去好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我会买土产回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  两个人和一只
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天一夜的温泉旅行开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在挺深的山里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是秘密旅行  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地换乘电车和巴士  哪里秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了  给我走快点  你们两个渣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点  不过天气放晴真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎两位远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记跟经纪人说我出来旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带您去房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点累  不过很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔远行一下也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁橱？什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在没人  先去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对  走吧  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极乐啊极乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你一只猫第一个下去泡算怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说我不是猫了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是什么！肥猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥…什么叫肥猫啊！肥猫！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底把高贵的我当成什么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫·一·只
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  别吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把水泡脏了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本就是陶器  才不会干那种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡得舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生那块像壁虎一样的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人似乎看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不知该往哪看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是不太会应付妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过名取先生大概…恨着妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了夏目  头泡晕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是女学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是有会有多愁善感的年纪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你突然冒出来很吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}  我跟你说过别吓夏目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我忘了他是个软弱的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}是名取先生驱使的妖怪之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好擦干的话  会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用管她  妖怪不会感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝牛奶是因为想喝啤酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒很好哦  要是夏目你也成年了该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以一起好好享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里…有什么从天花板上垂下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去馆内绕一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚泡完澡容易冷  你就先回房间等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生邀我是想来休养的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你还是要小心友人帐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还好好的在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  没跟名取先生说过友人帐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说  会被抢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他个性是那样  还是不会做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在这么说  等真的坦白了  以你的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又会整天烦恼他是不是因为友人帐才来跟你套近乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  这也挺麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消极的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个壁橱  里面是不是有老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有个壶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶？在壁橱里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  盖着盖子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  盖子上还有张快破掉的纸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来就是在这附近的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的那个挂着人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个壶  正好能装下一个人头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打开看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没趣  说不定里面装满了好吃的{\fscx90\fscy88\fn方正大黑_GBK\b0}藠{\r}头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会上当  哪有这么好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90\fscy88\fn方正大黑_GBK\b0}藠{\r}头怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  好  那就吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小猫多点一份刺身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还是有点挂心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在也只是看到身影  听到声音  没什么危害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你带我出来想快乐地旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情也没严重到要特意说出来把心情搞坏的地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  今天就别去想妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了  好困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟现在的监护人相处得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  他们对我很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是觉得疲于说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到我这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个的话  或许可以不用说谎地相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  小时候常因为能看见妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人说成是骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子  骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近经常会梦到那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子  骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说谎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听你在呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人啊  竟然会因为做梦而哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶的盖子打开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶？啊  之前说装{\fscx90\fscy88\fn方正大黑_GBK\b0}藠{\r}头的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该不是{\fscx90\fscy88\fn方正大黑_GBK\b0}藠{\r}头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不时会有响动  刚才盖子好像自己打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁橱里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看就知道盖子打开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为感觉有股不好的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空的  还是里面的东西跑出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个壶是被相当强的封印封住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得没什么需要特别注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能自己打开封印  应该是很强的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那封印是最近加上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  果然是个大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃了它吗  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个有友人帐的夏目大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您  请您把名字还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做澄江
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直是住在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类来了之后嫌我碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把我封印进壶里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您将名字还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  我对人类的村子就没有迷恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是您把名字还给我  我就离开此地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在深山中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没打算给这家旅馆添麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话  我也可以用友人帐命令你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不用命令  我也会从这房子里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么久以来  束缚住你的名字真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此我就无所畏惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不同  真温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一口吞了你让你少受点苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢  难得的佳肴  不会让你逃出这房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走  到尽头的那个房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为自己很了解妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  叫名取的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该告诉我们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打什么歪主意  别太小看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡完澡之后我准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这旅馆的后山有个伤害人类的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被别的驱魔师封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的驱魔师？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在完全封印妖怪之前  好像被它逃进这旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道夏目讨厌驱除妖怪  就说谎邀他来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他帮你驱除妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人已经成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道你这么高兴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就该好好跟你说清楚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我也有没告诉名取先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时  说谎已经变成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  名取先生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙  这次是我太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  用这整个房间的结界来封印妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}柊{\r}你去外面守着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真没趣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你哦  吃了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的人类  把你们都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣脱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名取先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你伤害夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找您好久了  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘了吗  您为我铺设了桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三只眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那时候的妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就由我带走清理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候跟那种大妖怪认识的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微帮了点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这么讲礼貌的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又随便跟妖怪扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会哭  会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会背叛  也会报恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人他只是来确认被封印的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:21:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为机会难得  他是想跟你说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也有很多话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有很多话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是对名取先生  还是藤原夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很想说  却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是害怕被人了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经习惯了被别人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有朝一日一定  一定能说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉希望他们知道我的真心的那些人们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  又把你卷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否不要放在心上  以后再来找我玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  第一次温泉旅行结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些急着想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着许多快乐的回忆  和想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从哪里说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:51.29,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}孵化雏子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子里的鸟巢里  只留下了一个蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  老师  你不是很闲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  叫我来孵化？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  变大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出  出生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子  我来取那个辰未的雏子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

